ISLAMABAD, Jun 4 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan on Thursday directed to further speed up the process of reforms in petroleum sector so as to bring about improvement in the sector and provide relief to the masses.
He was talking to Special Assistant to PM Nadeem Babar who called on him here and briefed him about the progress of ongoing reforms process in the petroleum sector.
